      "term" : "clinically significant disorder of mental health as specified",
      "definition" : "means one of\r\nthe following conditions, which is of sufficient severity to warrant ongoing\r\nmanagement, which may involve regular visits (for example, at least\r\nmonthly) to a psychiatrist, counsellor or general practitioner:\r\n(a) anxiety disorder;\r\n(b) depressive disorder; or\r\n(c) posttraumatic stress disorder."
    } ]
